00:08:23.442 --> 00:08:24.306
PETER LUBBERS: Exactly.

00:08:24.306 --> 00:08:26.540
KATHERINE MILLER: From a
pedagogical perspective for

00:08:26.540 --> 00:08:31.980
teachers to have that instant
feedback is really powerful.

00:08:31.980 --> 00:08:34.120
Is really powerful.

