00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:10.520
And I was just talking about,
you know, it'd be really cool

00:09:10.520 --> 00:09:13.230
to teach an HTML5 course.

00:09:13.230 --> 00:09:16.565
And so we were trying to think
of motivating examples.

00:09:16.565 --> 00:09:18.890
And we're like, well, let's
build some games.

00:09:18.890 --> 00:09:22.300
And then we got in contact
with Peter and Colt.

00:09:22.300 --> 00:09:24.620
And it's like, well, how do we
go about building games?

00:09:24.620 --> 00:09:25.740
I mean, we're not
game developers.

00:09:25.740 --> 00:09:27.140
