00:20:36.010 --> 00:20:40.510
And now you're teaching with
Udacity in this is much

00:20:40.510 --> 00:20:42.650
larger, more scaled
environment.

00:20:42.650 --> 00:20:44.920
What's that experience
been like?

00:20:44.920 --> 00:20:46.050
COLT MCANLIS: It's
been fantastic to

00:20:46.050 --> 00:20:47.690
be honest with you.

00:20:47.690 --> 00:20:49.110
Teaching at SMU was great.

00:20:49.110 --> 00:20:51.620
The fact that they have an
