line about what data you're

00:20:59.750 --> 00:21:05.180
serving that has to deal with
the curriculum for getting the

00:21:05.180 --> 00:21:06.990
piece of paper at the
end of things versus

00:21:06.990 --> 00:21:07.900
what's super relevant.

