00:21:31.640 --> 00:21:34.740
And the great part about
Udacity is it's

00:21:34.740 --> 00:21:36.430
like that on steroids.

00:21:36.430 --> 00:21:38.920
If you actually take our canvas
courses, you'll get

00:21:38.920 --> 00:21:41.850
sort of our cool little nuggets
of information about

00:21:41.850 --> 00:21:42.900
the games industry.

