00:22:35.236 --> 00:22:37.140
COLT MCANLIS: You and Calvin
had the hardest job.

00:22:37.140 --> 00:22:40.080
Because you had to translate
all this gobbledygook in my

00:22:40.080 --> 00:22:43.380
head and put it into
normal human speak.

00:22:43.380 --> 00:22:45.040
So hats off to these guys.

