more of that performance, is

00:49:38.890 --> 00:49:40.540
going to be your cap.

00:49:40.540 --> 00:49:42.840
And game developers are
constantly demanding more.

00:49:42.840 --> 00:49:46.160
So if you're kind of doing a
2D environment type game,

00:49:46.160 --> 00:49:47.210
HTML5 works really well.

00:49:47.210 --> 00:49:48.950
If you're really trying to do
something 3D and immersive,

00:49:48.950 --> 00:49:50.740
